This phase eliminates the most repetitive code in the backend. The key insight is that every controller follows one of two patterns, and inline route handlers can be extracted to controllers.

#### 2A. Create a shared error class to replace plain object throws

**New file:** `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\server\utils\AppError.js`

```js
export class AppError extends Error {
    constructor(status, message) {
        super(message);
        this.status = status;
        this.name = 'AppError';
    }
}
```

Then incrementally migrate services from:
```js
